                                <uv>

                                    <li>By Plane

                                        <p>
                                            <a href="https://airastana.com/global/en-us "> <em>Air Astana</em></a> is
                                            the national
                                            air carrier of Kazakhstan, based in Almaty. <br>
                                            It operates regular international and domestic flights on 64 routes from its
                                            main hub, Almaty International Airport, <br>
                                            and from a secondary hub, Nursultan Nazarbayev International Airport.
                                        </p>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>By Train

                                        <p>
                                            If you are already in another city of Kazakhstan, you can get to Almaty
                                            by <a href="https://bilet.railways.kz/?_locale=us"> <em>train</em></a>. <br>
                                            You will arrive in Almaty 1, or to
                                            Almaty 2, <br>
                                            it's  closer to downtown from which you can
                                            get to any part.
                                        </p>
                                    </li>

                                </uv>

