                            <uv>

                                <li>By Bus

                                    <p>
                                        <a href="https://alatransit.kz/en"> <i>There are plenty of
                                                bus
                                                routes </i> </a> for tourists to go anywhere for cheap price in the city
                                        of
                                        Almaty.
                                        <br> Today, fare payment is available with a transport card, as well as by means
                                        of a QR code. <br>
                                        There are the following mobile applications for this: Transcard, Kaspi.kz, <br>
                                        SMSBUS, Homebank, My Activ, My Beeline, Senim, Rakhmet, Astra Bus, Plus24
                                        (Kassa24), Qiwi and OYBY
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>On foot

                                    <p>
                                        A walk allows you to immerse yourself in the pleasure of traveling from one
                                        point to another. <br>
                                        You will get to know the city you are visiting better, besides, it's possible to
                                        talk with the locals to get acquainted with Kazakh culture,
                                        see amazing artistic architecture and just enjoy!
                                    </p>
                                </li>

